Usage

ec2-describe-instances | java ... com.novaordis.em.Ec2DescribeInstancesParser <options>

where the options are:

  --help - this help

  --filter|--filters <field=value>[,....]

  --list - outputs a space separated list

            --list field1:field2:....

    Example:

            ... --filter state=running --list name:public-ip


  --table - outputs a table with headers

            --table field1:field2:....

    Example:

            ... --filter state=running --table name:public-ip
